summary: Check PrepareArtifact plugin
description: |
    Test coverage for all artifact provider types:
    - koji provider (fetch from Koji build ID)
    - file provider (local RPM file)
    - repository-url provider (remote .repo file)
    - All providers combined in a single prepare step
test: ./test.sh
duration: 20m
# TODO: Enable the tests for other provision formats
# TODO: Could we test provision local safely?
tag+:
  - provision-only
  - provision-container
adjust:
  # TODO: Handle centos artifacts also
  - when: distro != fedora
    enabled: false
    because: Need to dynamically handle centos/brew/epel artifacts somehow also
